LEX Escrow


"Payer" is person

"Seller" is person

"Agent" is person

"Amount" is amount

"Fee" is amount


The Payer pays Amount into escrow, appoints the Seller, appoints the Agent, and fixes the Fee


CLAUSE: Pay Out

The Agent may pay from escrow the Fee to themselves, and afterwards pay the remainder of the escrow to the Seller


CLAUSE: Pay Back

The Agent may pay from escrow the Fee to themselves, and afterwards pay the remainder of the escrow to the Payer


